<div id="userManual">
	<p>
		<b>1. How to register a new Patient?</b>
	</p>
	<p>From "Patients" Menu, select "New Patient Registration"</p>
	<p>
		<b>2. How to search Patient records?</b>
	</p>
	<p>From "Patients" Menu, select "Search Patients". Enter value for
		any of the fields or a combination of fields to search and fetch
		matching patient records.</p>
	<p>
		<b>3. How to add a Doctor consultation?</b>
	</p>
	<p>Search patients as detailed before. Once you get the required
		patient details, open its patient registration form and select button
		"Add Visit"</p>

</div>